               <birth when="1408">He was born  in the district of <placeName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LOC6136Waj">Waǧ</placeName> in <date>1408</date>
               </birth>
              
               <floruit when="1440" evidence="internal">He was the ninth abbot of the monastery of <placeName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/INS0341DL">Dabra Libānos</placeName>. 
